<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" identifier="Q26_v3" title="Q26_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una ficha de veterinaria se registra la siguiente pauta para administrar un sedante:<br />• Fórmula de cálculo: dosis (en gramos) = <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>0,03</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mtext>masa del animal (en kg)</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.<br />• Masa del perro: 64 kg.<br /><br />¿Cuál es la dosis de sedante que debe recibir el perro?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">0,192 g<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al reemplazar la masa del perro en la fórmula, se obtiene <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mtext>dosis</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,03</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>0,192</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, esta opción no corresponde a la dosis indicada por la pauta.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">1,92 g<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Aplicando la fórmula dada: <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mtext>dosis</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,03</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, la dosis que debe recibir el perro es <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">19,2 g<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La pauta indica <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mtext>dosis</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,03</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>19,2</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, esta opción no satisface el cálculo pedido.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">2133,3 g<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Usando la fórmula de la ficha, <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mtext>dosis</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,03</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>2133,3</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, esta alternativa no corresponde a la dosis del perro.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar la fórmula</strong></p>
            <p>La ficha indica: <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mtext>dosis (en gramos)</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,03</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mtext>masa del animal (en kg)</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Reemplazar la masa del perro</strong></p>
            <p>Como la masa del perro es 64 kg, se reemplaza en la fórmula:</p>
            <p><m:math display="block"><m:mrow><m:mtext>dosis</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,03</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>64</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular el producto</strong></p>
            <p>Primero, <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>192</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Como <m:math display="inline"><m:mn>0,03</m:mn></m:math> tiene dos cifras decimales, se ubica la coma dos lugares hacia la izquierda:</p>
            <p><m:math display="block"><m:mrow><m:mn>0,03</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,92</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Escribir la unidad</strong></p>
            <p>La dosis se expresa en gramos, así que el resultado es <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La dosis de sedante que debe recibir el perro es <strong><m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>1,92</m:mn><m:mtext> g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>